Btok updates the enhanced login feature and this update can greatly solve the problem of being unable to log into or register Btok. Here are the updates: 1. The enhanced login feature is now available. 2. Bug fixes.

Dear users we apologize for the delay in releasing the new version of Btok. During this period of time we have been working on developing new features to enhance your user experience. The main updates include a new decentralized wallet Btok Wallet and a new decentralized exchange Btok Swap . These new features provide a better digital currency trading experience. You can easily log into your Btok wallet using your email and password. Additionally you can quickly buy the tokens you want in Btok groups. Here are the updates: 1. Added the decentralized wallet Btok Wallet a secure and reliable non custodial decentralized WEB3 wallet. 2. Added the aggregated trading feature Btok Swap where users can swap tokens with one click in groups making transactions easier. 3. Bug fixes and experience upgrades.
